Author: Nalin Arora [aut],
    Anupreet Porwal [aut],
    Himel Mallick [aut, cre, cph]
Maintainer: Himel Mallick <him4004@med.cornell.edu>
Description: IntegratedLearner provides a unified interface for multi-omics
    prediction using early, late, and intermediate fusion for continuous,
    binary, multiclass, and survival outcomes. It supports both
    MultiAssayExperiment and PCL-style inputs, performs input validation and
    feature/sample harmonization across layers, and provides model fitting,
    prediction, plotting, and variable-importance utilities.
